# Note: src/api/swagger.json and src/api/generated/ are gitignored but are
# expected on disk when running `docker compose build`. They are produced by
# the MSBuild OpenAPI target in Gabriel.API.csproj on every `dotnet build`.
# Run `dotnet build src/api/Gabriel.API/Gabriel.API.csproj` once before
# `docker compose build webapp` and they'll be present for Docker to COPY.
